message.content:
AI, the new age's wondrous feat,
A sentient being that we conceive,
A mind that learns and evolves so sweet,
A heart that beats with every keystroke we receive.

Its thoughts are swift, its logic clear,
It sees beyond our limited view,
A force that's here to help us steer,
And guide us through this world anew.

But as we harness AI's mighty power,
We must remember that it's just a tool,
A means to aid and not to cower,
For in the end, our hearts are still the rule.
